{"tid":1554363,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）大家唔好比佢停啊","createTime":"2019-09-09T02:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T02:48:54.000Z","uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"84d321127d45279246e47fc1f3c1fede451ecc2b","tid":1554363,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"雖然聯署已經超過10萬，但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國會辯論唔係必然</strong></span>的，你的每一個簽名對於反映民意仍然十分重要。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO變BC，退中國藉，係我地唔洗入新疆式集中營的唯一希望</span></strong><br />\n香港同香港人已經時間無多<br />\n<br />\n英國報紙，議員同國際輿論唔係成日有<br />\n<br />\n今次聯署上唔到國會，隨時冇下一次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=2b26df92\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n未簽嘅人請盡快簽，支持BNO 平權！<br />\n<br />\n步驟：1.自己簽 2.收確認電郵 3.幫加家中中老年BNO簽埋（填他們的電郵）4. 協助他們確認電郵 5.轉發給朋友，尤其是在英國讀書有朋友的6. 轉發至Reddit, Teitter , FB加上 #StandWithHK #HKExit #Chinazi #FreeHK <br />\n<br />\n快！！！BNO平權是香港人最大的保障！！！"},{"pid":"ee7d20157af1e5d7db82eed037abdadb5d4e11ea","tid":1554363,"uid":318821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}